<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-education> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Department for Education is responsible for children’s services and education, including early years, schools, higher and further education policy in England. DfE is a ministerial department, supported by 14 agencies and public bodies ."@en .
